SIMPLE: consignify
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Consignify
<hw>Con*sig"ni*fy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>con-</ets> + <ets>sognify</ets>.]</ety> <def>To signify or denote
in combination with something else.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The cipher . . . only serves to connote and <qex>consignify</qex>,
and to change the value or the figures.</q> <rj><qau>Horne
Tooke.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Consignment</ent>⟦br⟧
